Name: PlasmaBeam Zombie
Difficulty: Medium
Connection: None
Summon: BeamGuy
Melee: No
Distance: Projectile
Type: Human, Undead
Brightmaps: Yes
Actor modification: No
ACS: No


A zombie with a Plasma Beam. Hard to avoid in open areas and does a lot of damage if sustained.
Kill it quickly or take cover to avoid being forced down.

A quick note, its attack doesn't display properly in Skulltag. Best used in (G)ZDoom.
